content: द्वापरः --रं [द्वाभ्यां सत्यत्रेतयुगाभ्यां परः पृषो° <ls>Tv.</ls>] {@--1@} <ab>N.</ab> of the third Yuga of the world; <ls>Ms. 9. 301.</ls> {@--2@} The side of a die marked with two points. {@--3@} Doubt, suspense, uncertainty.
